{{DISPLAYTITLE:Light_ChangeToValue}} {{Special|112|tag, value|Lighting|ChangeToValue}}
* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''value'': New light level
Sets the light level in a sector to ''value''.
==Examples== {{noexamples}}
== Conversions from linedef types == The following Doom map format types can be converted as Light_ChangeToValue: {| {{prettytable}} !Type!!Conversion!!Trigger |- |{{icon|Doom}} 13:W1 Light To 255 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 255) || Player Cross |- |{{icon|Doom}} 35:W1 Light To 35 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 35) || Player Cross |- |{{icon|Doom}} 79:WR Light To 35 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 35) || Player Cross, Repeatable |- |{{icon|Doom}} 81:WR Light To 255 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 255) || Player Cross, Repeatable |- |{{icon|Doom}} 138:SR Light To 255 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 255) || Player Use, Repeatable |- |{{icon|Doom}} 139:SR Light To 35 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 35) || Player Use, Repeatable |- |{{icon|Boom}} 170:S1 Light To 35 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 35) || Player Use |- |{{icon|Boom}} 171:S1 Light To 255 || Light_ChangeToValue (tag, 255) || Player Use |}
